projects.title: Calculator App
projects.description: I really enjoyed creating this application. I ran into a few issues with math logic trying to make sure I when the correct button was pushed the correct mathematical process was implmented. In all I learned how interact with DOM and Debug better.

projects.title: Star Wars App
projects.description: This was a tough App, A lot of banging my head on the wall. I had a few issues grabbing the information from the Api and displaying it in the table. I learned how to comb through an Api and grab the information I needed to display in the table. I really enjoyed the process of learning how Api's work and  how to use them.
